  {*}/Exch-T-bone-V       Blood                 $(0.18 / 365)

  {*}/C-marrow            C-marrow                  ---
  {*}/T-marrow            T-marrow                  ---
  {Pu}/Liver0             Blood                     0.462
  {Pu}/Liver1             Blood                     0.462
  {Pu}/Liver2             Blood                     0.462
  {^Pu}/Liver1            Liver1                    ---
  {^Pu}/Liver2            Liver2                    ---
